      "message": "I\u0027m totally open to other ideas for formats for specifying time ranges.  I tried to be pretty general, but a lot of it is probably unnecessary, eg. we\u0027ll probably never need seconds (and maybe not minutes), and it seems unlikely that we need multiple windows in the same day, although I did that so that we could support running between eg. 10pm and 2am, by specifying 22:00:00-23:59:59 and 00:00:00-02:00:00.  Another awkwardness is the validation which limits hours to 0-23 and minutes/seconds to 0-59; that could result in some rollers exiting the roll window if they happen to cycle during that one missing second in the example above.",
